snippet.textDisplay:
my feedback on improving fortnite to attract more players:
1) make something so players can make their own skins~ e.g clothes, different features of different skins and more. like Deadpool mixed with drift or something original .
2)make it possible to make your own server for free~ youtubers can do more with being able to make their own servers.
3)make colour customizing options ~ e.g Deadpool can be green .
4)add more vehicles into fortnite: cars, dump trucks, jets ?
5) add in a new gun or material for building
6) make fortnite have more bases/ interesting landing spots
7) add some power ups or boost in to the game
8) make a NEW different game mode ~original~
9) add a Lamborghini ~ sounds good to me~
10) add more things to do with life events like corona virus .
that's my feedback~ hope it helps.
